OL,5, The family of a 54-year-old charity    
OL,6, rower found dead in his boat while     
OL,7, crossing the Atlantic are appealing for
OL,8, help to bring his body home.           
OL,10,FMichael Holt, from Porthmadog, Gwynedd,
OL,11,Ffell ill about 700 miles (1,126km) into
OL,12,Fthe voyage and was found by a fishing  
OL,13,Fvessel crew that sailed to his aid.    
OL,15,FHe had type 1 diabetes and could not   
OL,16,Fget insurance for the journey.         
OL,18,FHis boat has now been towed to Cape    
OL,19,FVerde off western Africa and his family
OL,20,Fare raising money for his repatriation.
